ComicInfo.Summary: A lot of home truths get told when Francine and Katchoo argue about the states of their lives. In Houston a drunk Katchoo skulks around her own exhibition. David arrives in his usually jolly manner she cuts hims down and stomps away. A beautiful older woman approaches David and asks if that was Katina. When he says it is she gives him her card to give her. It is Carolyn Hobbs of the New Hobbs Foundation wishing to be her benefactor. David is blown away by it. Freddie and Casey appear and she stays with David while Freddie catches up with Katchoo. At the bar Katchoo's is getting more drunk when a man who looks like John Cleese tries to chat her up and gets shot down swiftly. Freddie start to inquire about Francine but Katchoo is not in the mood for him. David hears a scream in the galley that sounds like Francine's and he runs toward it.
ComicInfo.Title: Talk To Me
